<div class="container">
<a href="https://crazeemedia.app.n8n.cloud/webhook/ai-tools" class="back-link">&larr; Back to AI Tools Hub</a>
<div class="header">
<h1>AI Regex Generator</h1>
<p>Describe what you want to match in plain English. Get a working regex with explanations and test cases.</p>
</div>
<div class="form-card">
<label>Describe what you want to match:</label>
<textarea id="desc" placeholder="e.g. Match email addresses that end with .edu or .org&#10;e.g. Extract phone numbers in format (xxx) xxx-xxxx&#10;e.g. Validate hex color codes like #FF0000"></textarea>
<label style="margin-bottom:10px">Quick examples:</label>
<div class="examples">
<button onclick="setExample('Match valid email addresses')">Email addresses</button>
<button onclick="setExample('Match US phone numbers in any format')">Phone numbers</button>
<button onclick="setExample('Match URLs starting with http or https')">URLs</button>
<button onclick="setExample('Match IPv4 addresses')">IP addresses</button>
<button onclick="setExample('Match dates in MM/DD/YYYY format')">Dates</button>
<button onclick="setExample('Match hex color codes like #FF0000 or #fff')">Hex colors</button>
<button onclick="setExample('Match strong passwords: 8+ chars, uppercase, lowercase, number, special char')">Passwords</button>
<button onclick="setExample('Match HTML tags and their content')">HTML tags</button>
</div>
<div class="lang-row">
<div>
<label>Primary language:</label>
<select id="lang">
<option value="python">Python</option>
<option value="javascript">JavaScript</option>
<option value="java">Java</option>
<option value="go">Go</option>
<option value="csharp">C#</option>
<option value="php">PHP</option>
<option value="ruby">Ruby</option>
<option value="rust">Rust</option>
</select>
</div>
<div>
<label>Use case:</label>
<select id="usecase">
<option value="match">Match / Find</option>
<option value="validate">Validate entire string</option>
<option value="extract">Extract / Capture groups</option>
<option value="replace">Search &amp; Replace</option>
</select>
</div>
</div>
<button type="submit" id="genBtn" onclick="generate()">Generate Regex</button>
</div>
