<h3>API Access</h3>
<p style="color:#aaa;font-size:0.9em">Use this tool programmatically via our free API:</p>
<code>curl -X POST https://crazeemedia.app.n8n.cloud/webhook/regex-api \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"description": "match email addresses", "language": "python"}'</code>
</div>
